        "text": "Chieh Hubert Lin1Hsin-Ying Lee2Yen-Chi Cheng3Sergey Tulyakov2Ming-Hsuan Yang1,4,.5 1UC Merced2Snap Research3CMU4Google Research5Yonsei University ",
